adjectives.description: womanlike (comparative more womanlike, superlative most womanlike)

entries.meaning: Befitting or characteristic of a woman.
Resembling a woman; feminine; (of a man) effeminate.

adverbs.description: womanlike (comparative more womanlike, superlative most womanlike)

entries.meaning: In a manner perceived to be characteristic of a woman.
examples: I really meant it for a compliment, and to put her in a good mood; but, woman-like, she took it the wrong way.
